The text you shared is talking about ChatGPT, an artificial intelligence model that can interact with people using text and generate various responses to prompts. The speaker suggests to teach the audience how to create a transformer-based language model, which is the base of how ChatGPT works. Since training it with the entire internet data is complex, he proposes to use a simplified data set called Tiny Shakespeare. Tiny Shakespeare is a single file that contains all works of William Shakespeare. In other words, it's a complete collection of Shakespeare's works put together in one document.